These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Transport: train, jet-ski, van, trike
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Transport:jet-ski##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Transport:train##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Transport:jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Transport:van##1
6. Transport:jet-ski is somewhere to the left of Transport:train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | van  | jet-ski | trike        | train |

