.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Pet: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
Flower: azalea, sunflower, poppy, tulip
1. Flower:tulip is somewhere between Flower:poppy and Pet:hedgehog##7
2. Pet:snake is somewhere to the left of Pet:dog##5
3. Pet:snake is somewhere to the right of Flower:tulip##5
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:snake##1
5. Flower:tulip is between Flower:poppy and Flower:sunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Flower   | sunflower   | tulip | poppy | azalea |

