.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Hobby: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
Flower: amaryllis, bellflower, balloon-flower, lily
1. Flower:lily is on the far left or far right##3
2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Flower:bellflower and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Flower:lily##1
4. Flower:balloon-flower is on the left of Flower:lily##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Flower:amaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Flower   | bellflower      | amaryllis   | balloon-flower | lily  |

